    "course_title": "INTERMEDIATE LABORATORY-MECHANICS AND MODERN PHYSICS",
    "description": "Experiments in modern physics, with discussion of statistical uncertainties and error analysis.  Propagation of error.  Available labs include gamma-ray spectroscopy, X-ray physics and diffraction, blackbody radiation, and Cavendish measurement of the gravitational constant G.",
